19
00:00:18,606 --> 00:00:20,441
<i>Terror at the Temple!</i>

20
00:00:20,483 --> 00:00:24,862
<i>The Jedi Temple is in disarray
after a vicious terrorist attack.</i>

21
00:00:25,029 --> 00:00:28,199
<i>Anakin Skywalker and Ahsoka Tano
set out to find the truth</i>

22
00:00:28,282 --> 00:00:31,118
<i>of who was really behind
this horrendous catastrophe.</i>

23
00:00:31,452 --> 00:00:36,123
<i>Their investigation led them to discover
the true saboteur, Letta Turmond.</i>

24
00:00:36,207 --> 00:00:39,377
<i>Now, the Jedi attempt to
return the Temple to normalcy.</i>

25
00:00:39,961 --> 00:00:43,965
<i>But first, Master Yoda must give a eulogy
to the fallen Jedi warriors.</i>

26
00:00:46,634 --> 00:00:48,970
One with the Force, they are.

27
00:00:49,220 --> 00:00:50,638
And our job it is

28
00:00:50,721 --> 00:00:54,559
to remember that we will, in time,
also pass on.

29
00:00:54,684 --> 00:00:59,188
Luminous beings are we,
but temporary vessels our bodies are.

30
00:00:59,480 --> 00:01:02,733
And we shall all find ourselves here,
in time.

31
00:01:03,693 --> 00:01:05,820
A moment of silence, I ask.

32
00:01:05,903 --> 00:01:08,739
To remember and to move on.

33
00:01:11,993 --> 00:01:14,245
You were close to one of them?

34
00:01:14,745 --> 00:01:17,498
Tutso Mara. We trained together.

35
00:01:18,541 --> 00:01:21,752
He taught me how to hold
my lightsaber correctly.

36
00:01:22,169 --> 00:01:25,089
Live for the living Jedi, we must.

37
00:01:26,757 --> 00:01:29,760
Live through us, forever they will.

38
00:01:51,574 --> 00:01:53,576
So what happens to Letta now?

39
00:01:53,701 --> 00:01:54,869
The bomber has been moved.

40
00:01:54,952 --> 00:01:57,204
Moved? Where?

41
00:01:57,288 --> 00:01:59,081
Why should she be moved?

42
00:01:59,206 --> 00:02:01,917
The Republic military
has taken her into custody.

43
00:02:02,126 --> 00:02:05,713
Ugh ! But why? This is a Jedi matter, isn't it?

44
00:02:05,963 --> 00:02:07,131
Clones were killed,

45
00:02:07,214 --> 00:02:10,384
which makes this terrorist attack
a military matter.

46
00:02:10,551 --> 00:02:14,221
An attack on the Jedi
is an attack on the Senate.

47
00:02:14,388 --> 00:02:17,558
Admiral Tarkin is right. Letta isn't a Jedi.

48
00:02:17,892 --> 00:02:20,728
It's not for us to be judge and jury
over a citizen of the Republic.

49
00:02:21,228 --> 00:02:25,107
If Letta's guilty, she's guilty,
and she should be dealt with.

50
00:02:25,232 --> 00:02:26,734
Calm down, Ahsoka.

51
00:02:26,776 --> 00:02:30,071
Remember, revenge is not the Jedi way.

52
00:02:31,822 --> 00:02:35,951
The evidence seems clear, Ahsoka.
Nothing will ever change.

53
00:02:36,911 --> 00:02:39,997
The Chancellor feels very strongly
that the Jedi be removed

54
00:02:40,081 --> 00:02:41,916
from as many military matters as possible.

55
00:02:43,584 --> 00:02:46,253
You yourselves said
that you're peacekeepers,

56
00:02:46,671 --> 00:02:48,339
not soldiers.

57
00:02:48,589 --> 00:02:51,300
I hope Chancellor Palpatine
knows what he's doing.

58
00:02:51,425 --> 00:02:55,262
I assure you that he rarely does anything
without a strategy.

59
00:03:01,102 --> 00:03:02,937
I have many things to attend to, Masters.

60
00:03:04,772 --> 00:03:05,981
Good day.

61
00:03:06,190 --> 00:03:07,316
Ahsoka.

62
00:03:11,612 --> 00:03:14,156
Go, be with your friend, Ahsoka.

63
00:03:17,118 --> 00:03:19,787
In ways, she is still very young.

64
00:03:19,870 --> 00:03:21,288
Indeed.

65
00:03:26,335 --> 00:03:28,170
-Company?
-Sure.

66
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:32,633
Every time I think about this,
I feel conflicted.

67
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:37,012
It's hard not to let feelings
turn into attachment and pain.

68
00:03:37,972 --> 00:03:41,851
Ahsoka, have you ever wondered if
it was right to ignore your emotions?

69
00:03:42,309 --> 00:03:46,897
My master would say our struggle as Jedi
is to move past them.

70
00:03:46,981 --> 00:03:49,024
You make it sound so easy.

71
00:03:49,358 --> 00:03:52,319
No, it isn't easy. But it's possible.

72
00:03:52,862 --> 00:03:55,656
Like when we were stuck inside
the battle tank on Geonosis.

73
00:03:55,740 --> 00:03:57,575
It was hard not to be afraid.

74
00:03:57,658 --> 00:03:59,910
Still, you and I got past it.

75
00:03:59,994 --> 00:04:02,246
And I guess we'll get past this.

76
00:04:02,371 --> 00:04:05,332
You've always been capable
of seeing things clearly.

77
00:04:06,751 --> 00:04:08,043
I guess I fooled you

78
00:04:08,169 --> 00:04:09,837
like I have everyone else.

79
00:04:10,337 --> 00:04:11,505
Yes, Master.

80
00:04:11,547 --> 00:04:13,507
<i>Ahsoka,
we're needed in the War Room.</i>

81
00:04:13,549 --> 00:04:15,843
<i>It appears the Separatists
have mounted another attack.</i>

82
00:04:15,926 --> 00:04:17,511
Coming, Master.

83
00:04:18,763 --> 00:04:21,849
Look, I have to believe
that, one way or another,

84
00:04:21,932 --> 00:04:24,685
this woman's going to pay for what she did.

85
00:04:25,311 --> 00:04:27,396
You shouldn't keep your master waiting.

86
00:04:35,237 --> 00:04:38,115
<i>We've uncovered
a Separatist plan of attack.</i>

87
00:04:38,741 --> 00:04:40,534
<i>We shall travel to the A no it system here,</i>

88
00:04:41,869 --> 00:04:43,704
<i>then move across to Saleucami.</i>

89
00:04:43,788 --> 00:04:45,873
So far out of our way?

90
00:04:45,915 --> 00:04:49,126
<i>Unfortunately we must avoid
these neutral systems.</i>

91
00:04:49,585 --> 00:04:50,920
<i>Excuse me, Master Jedi.</i>

92
00:04:51,045 --> 00:04:52,213
Yes, Admiral.

93
00:04:52,254 --> 00:04:56,550
<i>Commander Tano, your presence
is requested by prisoner Letta Turmond.</i>

94
00:04:56,592 --> 00:04:58,093
The prisoner from the hangar bombing?

95
00:04:58,219 --> 00:04:59,929
Why is she asking for Ahsoka?

96
00:05:00,095 --> 00:05:01,388
<i>Not exactly sure.</i>

97
00:05:01,430 --> 00:05:05,100
<i>But Commander Tano is the only person
the prisoner will speak to.</i>

98
00:05:05,226 --> 00:05:08,062
I'll report back with whatever I find out.

99
00:05:49,478 --> 00:05:50,521
<i>Yes?</i>

100
00:05:50,771 --> 00:05:53,816
<i>I'm Commander Tano.
Letta Turmond requested to see me.</i>

101
00:05:54,275 --> 00:05:57,820
<i>A lot of innocent people died in that blast.
Good job capturing her.</i>

102
00:05:59,655 --> 00:06:00,781
All right, scan her.

103
00:06:08,289 --> 00:06:11,000
<i>Leave your com link and lightsabers here.</i>

104
00:06:16,630 --> 00:06:18,132
Follow me.

105
00:06:42,448 --> 00:06:44,283
What do you want, Letta?

106
00:06:44,325 --> 00:06:46,535
I was told if I ever needed help,

107
00:06:46,660 --> 00:06:48,037
you were the Jedi to contact.

108
00:06:52,666 --> 00:06:54,710
Give us a minute, please.

109
00:06:58,339 --> 00:07:00,132
You don't have much time, Letta,

110
00:07:00,174 --> 00:07:04,011
so I suggest you get
whatever you have to say off your chest.

111
00:07:05,804 --> 00:07:09,516
The idea of feeding Jackar
the nano-droids was not mine.

112
00:07:09,558 --> 00:07:11,852
Why are you saying this now?

113
00:07:11,977 --> 00:07:13,687
Why didn't you reveal this before?

114
00:07:13,812 --> 00:07:15,981
Because my life is in danger.

115
00:07:16,190 --> 00:07:18,150
The person behind this
will be able to get to me

116
00:07:18,192 --> 00:07:20,069
unless you know the truth.

117
00:07:20,194 --> 00:07:21,654
Hmm. What's the truth?

118
00:07:22,571 --> 00:07:23,822
A Jedi.

119
00:07:23,864 --> 00:07:26,033
A Jedi showed me how to create the bomb

120
00:07:26,075 --> 00:07:27,868
and how to put the nano-droids in.

121
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:30,871
Why would a Jedi do this?

122
00:07:30,996 --> 00:07:33,666
There are some citizens
of the Republic, like myself,

123
00:07:33,707 --> 00:07:36,710
who believe the Jedi Order
is not what it used to be.

124
00:07:36,752 --> 00:07:38,545
The Jedi have become warmongers.

125
00:07:38,671 --> 00:07:40,714
They've become military weapons,

126
00:07:40,839 --> 00:07:43,759
and they're killing
when they should be keeping the peace.

127
00:07:44,009 --> 00:07:48,222
One of these Jedi agreed with us.
One of you wanted to make a statement,

128
00:07:48,722 --> 00:07:51,350
and was willing to attack
your own order to do it.

129
00:07:53,310 --> 00:07:54,395
Who?

130
00:07:54,478 --> 00:07:56,981
If you protect me, I will tell you.

131
00:07:57,064 --> 00:07:59,984
Because it is obvious to me
that I have been set up!

132
00:08:00,651 --> 00:08:03,570
Letta, you have to tell me
who is behind this.

133
00:08:07,074 --> 00:08:08,242
It's...

134
00:08:08,325 --> 00:08:10,244
Letta? Letta!

135
00:08:10,369 --> 00:08:11,412
Letta!

136
00:08:11,537 --> 00:08:16,417
<i>Prisoner health critical. Holding cell 1-7-3.</i>

137
00:08:16,542 --> 00:08:18,711
Commander Fox, the prisoner!

138
00:08:19,086 --> 00:08:20,421
Follow me.

139
00:08:24,091 --> 00:08:25,175
Letta!

140
00:08:32,516 --> 00:08:35,102
I don't know what happened.

141
00:08:35,227 --> 00:08:37,438
Commander, she's dead.

142
00:08:37,938 --> 00:08:40,399
I can't say I blame you, Commander Tano,

143
00:08:40,441 --> 00:08:43,444
but all the same, you're under arrest.

144
00:08:43,569 --> 00:08:47,114
I... No, no, I did not do this!

145
00:09:16,143 --> 00:09:18,812
Admiral Tarkin,
I don't know what happened.

146
00:09:18,896 --> 00:09:22,775
I went in the room to talk to Letta
and she said she was afraid of a Jedi.

147
00:09:25,819 --> 00:09:29,156
You don't have to tell me
any more, Commander Tano.

148
00:09:29,615 --> 00:09:31,492
-I don't?
-No.

149
00:09:31,575 --> 00:09:33,035
There are recorders in every room.

150
00:09:35,829 --> 00:09:38,665
Curiously, the sound isn't working
on this one.

151
00:09:41,335 --> 00:09:43,712
It seems the Jedi she was afraid of

152
00:09:43,796 --> 00:09:44,838
was you.

153
00:09:44,922 --> 00:09:47,216
I did not kill that woman!

154
00:09:47,299 --> 00:09:48,926
You were the only one there!

155
00:09:49,009 --> 00:09:50,177
I know that you were upset

156
00:09:50,260 --> 00:09:52,679
when this woman
was taken into custody by the military.

157
00:09:53,222 --> 00:09:54,807
That means nothing!

158
00:09:54,890 --> 00:09:56,100
I beg to differ.

159
00:09:56,183 --> 00:09:59,853
It was someone else, Admiral !
Someone I didn't see!

160
00:09:59,978 --> 00:10:03,190
You know that is very difficult
for me to believe.

161
00:10:03,357 --> 00:10:08,445
This is a secure facility.
We do not have just anyone running about.

162
00:10:08,529 --> 00:10:10,864
And if there was someone else,

163
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:13,075
why did you not sense them?

164
00:10:22,376 --> 00:10:25,462
I said my Padawan is in there.

165
00:10:25,546 --> 00:10:26,922
Now step aside.

166
00:10:27,047 --> 00:10:29,883
<i>General Skywalker,
Admiral Tarkin has ordered</i>

167
00:10:29,967 --> 00:10:32,553
<i>that no one be allowed in there.</i>

168
00:10:33,095 --> 00:10:35,139
I don't care what she's accused of.

169
00:10:35,222 --> 00:10:37,391
Let me in.

170
00:10:42,020 --> 00:10:45,149
Sorry, sir. The Admiral's orders stand.

171
00:10:45,732 --> 00:10:49,778
This is now a military operation,
and under his jurisdiction.

172
00:11:17,931 --> 00:11:19,641
A key card?

173
00:11:19,808 --> 00:11:22,686
Master, I knew you wouldn't let me down.

174
00:11:34,114 --> 00:11:37,117
I wonder what you have planned.

175
00:11:47,211 --> 00:11:50,297
Oh, no, this does not look good.

176
00:11:59,056 --> 00:12:00,724
My lightsabers?

177
00:12:04,978 --> 00:12:07,147
Hello? Who is this?

178
00:12:07,731 --> 00:12:09,650
Why are you helping me?

179
00:12:11,568 --> 00:12:13,654
-What's going on here?
-It wasn't me!

180
00:12:18,700 --> 00:12:21,453
Alert! Alert!
The Jedi prisoner has escaped!

181
00:12:39,346 --> 00:12:40,555
Commander Tano, stop!

182
00:12:44,518 --> 00:12:46,436
She's heading north in the prison corridor.

183
00:12:46,603 --> 00:12:47,896
<i>Cut her off!</i>

184
00:12:47,980 --> 00:12:49,314
Copy that.

185
00:13:10,252 --> 00:13:11,378
Oh, no.

186
00:13:18,635 --> 00:13:21,221
Suspect has killed three clones. Code red!

187
00:13:21,305 --> 00:13:23,223
If you see the target, shoot to kill.

188
00:13:23,974 --> 00:13:25,434
Belay that order, Commander Fox!

189
00:13:25,892 --> 00:13:27,728
She's killed troopers!

190
00:13:27,811 --> 00:13:31,690
I know Commander Tano.
She would never do something like this.

191
00:13:31,773 --> 00:13:33,817
-Then who did?
-Quiet!

192
00:13:35,193 --> 00:13:38,030
Ahsoka! It's me, Anakin !

193
00:13:41,825 --> 00:13:43,076
Stop running!

194
00:13:44,453 --> 00:13:47,789
You can't help me, Master.
Someone's setting me up!

195
00:13:48,457 --> 00:13:49,875
I believe you, Ahsoka!

196
00:13:51,752 --> 00:13:53,587
But no one else will!

197
00:13:56,548 --> 00:13:58,467
Keep searching until we find her.

198
00:13:58,592 --> 00:13:59,718
Rex, call security.

199
00:13:59,801 --> 00:14:02,929
Tell them we need to search
the entire base. Now!

200
00:14:03,430 --> 00:14:05,599
General Skywalker has just issued

201
00:14:05,682 --> 00:14:08,352
an all-points bulletin
on Commander Ahsoka Tano.

202
00:14:08,435 --> 00:14:09,853
She's killed three clones

203
00:14:09,936 --> 00:14:12,856
and should be considered
armed and dangerous.

204
00:14:26,995 --> 00:14:29,039
The prisoner was just spotted
in the east wing.

205
00:14:29,122 --> 00:14:30,832
Cell block 1218-11.

206
00:15:15,335 --> 00:15:18,505
Come on, Grizzer,
there's nothing here.

207
00:15:25,429 --> 00:15:28,140
There she is! Quick!
Stop her before she gets to the ship!

208
00:16:01,298 --> 00:16:03,425
All right, don't lose her.
We'll be right there.

209
00:16:03,550 --> 00:16:05,135
- What's going on?
- We've found her.

210
00:16:05,218 --> 00:16:07,053
She's heading towards
the industrial pipeline.

211
00:16:07,220 --> 00:16:09,890
Set weapons to stun. I want her alive!

212
00:16:54,935 --> 00:16:58,188
Do not shoot to kill ! Do not shoot to kill!

213
00:16:58,480 --> 00:17:00,524
Try to box her in ! Don't let her escape!

214
00:17:00,607 --> 00:17:02,317
Tell me what you see, Odd Ball.

215
00:17:15,956 --> 00:17:17,958
She's moving west
along the central viaduct.

216
00:17:32,472 --> 00:17:33,890
All right, we've got her now.

217
00:17:47,487 --> 00:17:49,155
This'll knock her off her feet!

218
00:18:07,424 --> 00:18:09,175
Not so fast, Commander!

219
00:18:31,698 --> 00:18:32,699
Ahsoka!

220
00:20:09,045 --> 00:20:11,589
Ahsoka, what are you doing?

221
00:20:12,382 --> 00:20:14,634
You didn't even try to come and help me!

222
00:20:14,759 --> 00:20:16,219
They wouldn't let me in to talk to you!

223
00:20:16,302 --> 00:20:18,304
You could have if you'd tried!

224
00:20:18,513 --> 00:20:20,765
How would that look, Ahsoka? Huh?

225
00:20:21,099 --> 00:20:23,601
Forcing my way in
would've made you look even more guilty.

226
00:20:23,852 --> 00:20:25,770
I'm not guilty!

227
00:20:26,187 --> 00:20:28,356
Then we have to prove you're innocent.

228
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:30,859
The only way we can do that
is by going back.

229
00:20:30,942 --> 00:20:33,111
I don't know who to trust.

230
00:20:33,403 --> 00:20:37,365
Listen, I would never let anyone
hurt you, Ahsoka. Never.

231
00:20:37,449 --> 00:20:40,785
But you need to come back
and make your case to the Council.

232
00:20:41,202 --> 00:20:46,374
No! I'm not going to take the fall
for something I didn't do!

233
00:20:46,666 --> 00:20:50,462
I am ordering you to put down
your lightsaber and come with me! Now!

234
00:20:51,254 --> 00:20:52,297
Trust me.

235
00:20:52,380 --> 00:20:54,716
General Skywalker, where are you?

236
00:20:54,883 --> 00:20:56,468
I do trust you.

237
00:20:56,551 --> 00:21:00,847
But you know as well as I do
that no one else will believe me.

238
00:21:04,768 --> 00:21:07,771
Anakin, you have to trust me now.

239
00:21:08,354 --> 00:21:09,647
Ahsoka, I do trust you!

240
00:21:09,814 --> 00:21:11,399
I know you do.

241
00:21:12,942 --> 00:21:14,736
Wish me luck.

242
00:21:14,760 --> 00:21:19,760
http://hiqve.com/

